        </div>
      </a>
      <a class="card" href="#">
        <div class="card-img" style="background-image:url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1503676260728-1c00da094a0b?w=600&q=80&auto=format&fit=crop')"><span class="card-pill badge badge-light">Resource</span></div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <div class="card-type">Downloadable</div>
          <div class="card-title">Coaching Conversations Toolkit</div><p class="card-desc">Frameworks and prompts to run better developmental conversations.</p>
          <div class="card-meta"><div class="line"><i class="fa-solid fa-file-lines"></i> PDF · 18 pages</div><div class="line"><i class="fa-solid fa-tag"></i> £0 for members</div></div><div class="card-tags"><span class="topic-tag sm">Coaching</span><span class="topic-tag sm">Leadership</span></div>
        </div>
      </a>
      <a class="card" href="#">
        <div class="card-img" style="background-image:url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1573497019940-1c28c88b4f3e?w=600&q=80&auto=format&fit=crop')"><span class="card-pill badge badge-light">Service</span></div>
