        </div>
      </a>
      <a class="card" href="#">
        <div class="card-img" style="background-image:url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1481627834876-b7833e8f5570?w=600&q=80&auto=format&fit=crop')"><span class="card-pill badge badge-light">Knowledge Hub</span></div>
        <div class="card-body">
